### 8-1) A가 B,D를 기존 방에 초대 → 기존 방 재활성(UPDATED_GROUP)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/rooms/{{roomABDEFGH}}/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userIds": [ {{userBId}}, {{userDId}} ]
}
> {%
    client.test("UPDATED_GROUP 기대", function() {
        client.assert(response.body.outcome === "UPDATED_GROUP", "outcome = " + response.body.outcome);
    });
%}

### 9) A의 채팅방 목록 조회 (시각 확인용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/chat/rooms?page=0&size=50
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}

### 10) (사전) A -> D 친구 요청
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/send
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenA}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverId": {{userDId}}
}

### 10-1) D가 받은 요청 목록에서 A의 요청 id 찾기
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/received
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenD}}

> {%
    const arr = response.body || [];
    const userAId = Number(client.global.get("userAId"));
    const found = arr.find(x => x.requesterId === userAId);
    if (!found) {
        client.test("A->D 요청이 목록에 있어야 함", function(){ client.assert(false, "A->D 요청 못 찾음"); });
    } else {
        client.global.set("reqAD", found.id);
    }
%}

### 10-2) D가 수락
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/friends/requests/{{reqAD}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenD}}

